00:37:41.890 --> 00:37:49.250
that -- You know, I draw these
kind of crazy letterforms,

00:37:49.250 --> 00:37:52.360
you know, that verge
on abstraction,

00:37:52.360 --> 00:37:56.750
and then I print
them individually.

00:37:56.750 --> 00:37:59.460
But then when I print texts,

00:37:59.460 --> 00:38:03.460
I design pretty traditional
