dot and pull it a little.

00:43:05.140 --> 00:43:08.420
And it's just horrible.

00:43:08.420 --> 00:43:12.620
So by the time I'm done with
the day, all I want to do is

00:43:12.620 --> 00:43:16.740
like feel some oil on my
hands, you know, or something

00:43:16.740 --> 00:43:18.410
and go to my print shop.

00:43:18.410 --> 00:43:22.490
So it's kind of nice
that I get to split that.

00:43:22.490 --> 00:43:24.440
But yeah, no.

00:43:24.440 --> 00:43:25.740
Yeah?

